{"tid":441374,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]人整啫喱我整啫喱，點解我件啫喱屎色既？","createTime":"2017-10-19T14:56:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T16:08:43.000Z","uid":43041,"like":348,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"22079bb30bacbb12b147f85a85a55f49a1ebbc2a","tid":441374,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:56:24.000Z","msg":"話說上網見到個簡單易整既甜品叫咩紅茶啫喱<br />\n話好簡單咁用茶包沖出黎既紅茶溝盒啫喱粉就得<br />\n理想示意圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hvcqszwx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhvcqszwx&h=72f2fc86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ndlwr7xv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fndlwr7xv&h=d7f453a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇落一d都唔難咁我就極速試下<br />\n無食譜上既牌子求其用屋企既紅茶包就算<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/trbi50s8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftrbi50s8&h=805ca399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用450ml度既熱水沖茶，放4個茶包<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9nejvdih\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9nejvdih&h=495d59b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10分鐘後倒落兩個杯度<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/usv6oref\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fusv6oref&h=d27de25d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n倒入啫喱粉，攪下佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5lo7ut64\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5lo7ut64&h=151987cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mgipact4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmgipact4&h=d0b773f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n放入雪櫃雪左幾個鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pbz5lngi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpbz5lngi&h=64a2cb75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仆街點解隻色咁撚樣既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔透既？<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/13d0ljo2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F13d0ljo2&h=bebdf6df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tm05ko3n\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftm05ko3n&h=3073d67a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tgpr4eqk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftgpr4eqk&h=bb70cf63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然食落去唔差無怪味，但點解一d都唔透明仲要係實屎色既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我邊度做錯左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11982752681bfe8da982554732974e3e204ca259","tid":441374,"uid":56878,"like":127,"dislike":1,"score":126,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:57:56.000Z","msg":"太濃"},{"pid":"2152caa468f225bbcd6d5d6e36a00d3de4082423","tid":441374,"uid":75100,"like":147,"dislike":0,"score":147,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:58:21.000Z","msg":"可能4個茶包太多? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實1-2個茶包都沖到好多ml濃既"},{"pid":"3f73dba0b8c3d1ab47cabfa1ad346ac82c966631","tid":441374,"uid":35408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:59:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能4個茶包太多? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實1-2個茶包都沖到好多ml濃既</blockquote><br />\n茶包減半"},{"pid":"889c98bfd3c9e304f482b0ddd3ff696f2c986467","tid":441374,"uid":58140,"like":408,"dislike":1,"score":407,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:00:23.000Z","msg":"濃撚到可以召喚腎者之石"},{"pid":"d1c692c09c75f3e31fe5732564563e42f40b57cc","tid":441374,"uid":15696,"like":101,"dislike":1,"score":100,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:01:43.000Z","msg":"1. 睇色都知...粉太多<br />\n2. 太實色.....太多茶"},{"pid":"da4ab2cea76023cb63a670d677b6acb811d6767c","tid":441374,"uid":36178,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:02:14.000Z","msg":"輕紅茶, 杯紅茶用清水以1:5再開"},{"pid":"37425bc98fe7bcb34948b04bebead1043d10c014","tid":441374,"uid":57300,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:04:46.000Z","msg":"一個茶包大約沖220ml嘅茶"},{"pid":"fd57f429dcd6ebe59a6173bae88670f7a7a0a542","tid":441374,"uid":36178,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:07:22.000Z","msg":"一盒啫仔粒開到4-5杯啫仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1069be63d7352ae5666ff46a3898a5b4d3fe3be0","tid":441374,"uid":43041,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:08:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可能4個茶包太多? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實1-2個茶包都沖到好多ml濃既</blockquote><br />\n茶包減半</blockquote><br />\n個食譜話一份就要用4個茶包啦，而我只係用左兩包咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/19/230713_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F19%2F230713_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c69d516d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78d9174958485661324bba23870d1b74c1eab5b9","tid":441374,"uid":30316,"like":318,"dislike":1,"score":317,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:09:08.000Z","msg":"因為你唔係用 Lipton <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba0cc97e9a05c23bbc82fa9313b08ba95a759e5","tid":441374,"uid":43041,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:09:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>濃撚到可以召喚腎者之石</blockquote><br />\n話雖如此，食落去都係茶味淡淡地<br />\n但唔敢再加茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdbfb7798f074d5b8663c44a5df06441d445ddf5","tid":441374,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:11:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 睇色都知...粉太多<br />\n2. 太實色.....太多茶</blockquote><br />\n我除左茶包分量減半，其餘都跟食譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來唔同牌子沖出黎效果咁唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4410b29479457cc0b0f5df7fa3754469d89d87ad","tid":441374,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:12:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>輕紅茶, 杯紅茶用清水以1:5再開</blockquote><br />\n依家先見到寫住輕紅茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來連茶包都有分種類"},{"pid":"4113c720971d8d21baf927947dd3eb718e6dbf2e","tid":441374,"uid":43041,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:13:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個茶包大約沖220ml嘅茶</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我見份食譜寫4個茶包225ml水<br />\n屌原來人地有個輕字係前面"},{"pid":"63ecc4472eda4ea873a850963fa898e942d77a66","tid":441374,"uid":41765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:13:27.000Z","msg":"Breakfast tea 好濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445ee476b15472322d213b9313804070f1226486","tid":441374,"uid":41765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:14:35.000Z","msg":"你試下用Earl grey la"},{"pid":"4451fc3cf486e47c81c50a068eca20782c5f3b81","tid":441374,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:14:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一盒啫仔粒開到4-5杯啫仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以為跟食譜就得，唔怪得咁甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b0249849a1cde3d9247b28dc54536dbd4412c4","tid":441374,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:15:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>輕紅茶, 杯紅茶用清水以1:5再開</blockquote><br />\n依家先見到寫住輕紅茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來連茶包都有分種類<